headline: BMO downgrades Dollar Tree citing digital gaps and risks on margin
summary: Investing.com -- BMO Capital Markets downgraded Dollar Tree to Underperform from Market Perform, saying the stock’s valuation and earnings expectations look stretched given risks around digital strategy and margin expansion.Shares of the retailer were down 1.11% in premarket trading on Friday.
